  "title": "Round 3 Experiment 2: Comb-Filtered Elevation Features",
  "description": "Replace the simple spectral-slope style elevation residual with a comb-response residual that measures periodic spectral structure across frequency channels.",
  "rationale": "This tests whether a richer fixed spectral operator improves elevation cues more than the current slope-like summary.",
